==September==
* '''?''' - [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] is admitted into [[King Edward's School]] after passing the entrance exam.

==Late==<!--perhaps September, see Reader's Companion p. lxxviii-->
* '''?''' - The Tolkiens move from [[Sarehole]] to [[Moseley]] to be closer to [[Birmingham]] and [[King Edward's School]].
